-- ISAF Says Civilian Contractor Shot Dead in Eastern Afghanistan
-- B y   E l t a f   N a j a f i z a d a
-- 2013-03-08T14:43:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-03-08/isaf-says-civilian-contractor-shot-dead-in-eastern-afghanistan.html
A civilian contractor with the
International Security Assistance Force was shot dead today in
eastern Afghanistan, the ISAF said.  The attack was carried out by individuals wearing Afghan
National Army uniforms, the ISAF said in an e-mailed statement,
without providing more information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
